description:
Get your API key at https://api.bitext.com/#/signup/api

Contact us at info@bitext.com

You can use this REST API to perform:

Sentiment Analysis: Structure every part of an opinion into positive/neutral/negative, identify the topic of the opinion, the sentiment expression used, and get a numeric value for each of the sentiment-bearing phrases. 

Entity Extraction: Extract from text names, places, firms, twitter users, and others.

Categorization: Classify text using a custom build taxonomy

Concept Analysis: Linguistically based structuring text.
